headline.print_headline: Congress Crams Unfinished Agenda Into Final Days
headline.main: Congress Crams Unfinished Agenda Into Final Days

lead_paragraph: Like a student who waited until the night before a deadline, lawmakers resuming work Monday will try to cram two years of leftover business into two weeks, while also seeking to avoid a government shutdown.
